{"tid":2492041,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"攞到公屋的抉擇│獲派筍盤公屋230呎單位 4口家嫌細想過唔要","createTime":"2021-04-16T18:57:39.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-17T02:12:23.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":239,"uniUserReply":80,"replies":[{"pid":"6aac90ed75ab25a9626fe46fae852865cb90b45f","tid":2492041,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T18:57:39.000Z","msg":"施先生是汕尾人，05年透過人才引進計劃申請到港工作，負責維修遊艇，再加上兼職銷售船票給自由行客人，月入接近三萬元。<br />\n<br />\n他09年結婚，有兩名分別5和12歲子女。一家四口住尖沙咀二百呎劏房，月租$12000。<br />\n<br />\n「居家優住，近朱者赤，近墨者黑，我希望子女在尖沙咀居住，交往的人也比較有文化，不會好像深水埗般品流複雜，所以便唯有捱貴租。」<br />\n<br />\n13年，他開始申請公屋，等了差不多8年，去年聖誕節收到通知，獲派深水埗的海達邨。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_782178_0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_782178_0&d=8tl7d8txXkgslZB5fT8CL8sFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=4eba5d76\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_782178_0&h=ee65b2df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_782178_0</a>"},{"pid":"00113caae582a9964774b9d05b1f0678cbc40a61","tid":2492041,"uid":38904,"like":200,"dislike":3,"score":197,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T18:59:43.000Z","msg":"屌你老母死支那狗有單位都重咁撚多嗲"},{"pid":"df5507e71ad08f8a3ef3f3a5b716137bcb4e2e30","tid":2492041,"uid":157483,"like":3,"dislike":43,"score":-40,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T19:01:57.000Z","msg":"家嫌 睇錯林家謙"},{"pid":"cbebb1122ad701344578876f332b3282a250123a","tid":2492041,"uid":128102,"like":80,"dislike":0,"score":80,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T19:04:56.000Z","msg":"學某膠官話齋<br />\n最好既方法係離開香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1902f6eda4418397b46f58a3955f6e37669561bc","tid":2492041,"uid":285559,"like":231,"dislike":1,"score":230,"citedBy":9,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T19:05:27.000Z","msg":"居家優住，近朱者赤，近墨者黑，我希望子女在尖沙咀居住，交往的人也比較有文化，不會好像深水埗般品流複雜，所以便唯有捱貴租。<br />\n<br />\n佢d仔女真係慘 個老豆咁on9 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><im